    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为袭击指挥官！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374290/extras/569350582c887a6473472e06bb473ace.poster.avif?t=1721990352\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374290/extras/569350582c887a6473472e06bb473ace.webm?t=1721990352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374290/extras/569350582c887a6473472e06bb473ace.mp4?t=1721990352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>浑身甲壳的强大英雄们正要发起一次袭击，凡是海岸上闪闪发光的好东西都不放过。它们个个受贪婪驱使，因此很容易被敌人牵着鼻子走并被智取。因此，它们需要您来当军师，帮助它们应对复杂多变的战斗情况，最终碾压敌人！<br><br>慎重安排英雄的位置，指引它们在愈发恶劣的环境中穿梭自如，这些英雄会无脑打击任何接近它们的东西！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>边玩边使小队进化！</strong></h2>海量升级可供选择，把您的螃蟹变成强大的特别战斗单位：有一夫当关的肉装坦克蟹，有为小队疗伤的狡猾治疗蟹，有足以重创敌人的精锐战斗蟹，还有无所不能的奇异混合体蟹！每升一级都能让您进一步自定义螃蟹，而每一次胜利都能让您获得古代器物。<br><br>您可以不断尝试，找出游戏的制胜组合，螃蟹们相信您的判断！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>运用元素力量！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374290/extras/10f37fb1226494c8bb30ad9821ae2333.poster.avif?t=1721990352\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374290/extras/10f37fb1226494c8bb30ad9821ae2333.webm?t=1721990352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374290/extras/10f37fb1226494c8bb30ad9821ae2333.mp4?t=1721990352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>神秘的元素之灵不知疲倦地守护着海岸，它们拥有各自的领地——从海底深处到天空中灼热的太阳。贪婪也是其中之一，它驱使所有生物囤积闪亮的宝藏，您勇敢的螃蟹小队自然也受它影响。<br>元素们喜欢勇敢者，它们愿意助您一臂之力。调和您的甲壳英雄，让它们掌握元素之力并以此击败敌人！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374290/extras/720570379829bb018160b6e113875b7a.avif?t=1721990352\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>结合不同元素，创造压倒性的组合技！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374290/extras/03452c9cf77beff2e6e43a3a09113d22.poster.avif?t=1721990352\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374290/extras/03452c9cf77beff2e6e43a3a09113d22.webm?t=1721990352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374290/extras/03452c9cf77beff2e6e43a3a09113d22.mp4?t=1721990352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>这些元素个个都很强大，但被您的小队组合在一起后会更强大！让您的螃蟹与不同元素调和，获得威力巨大的元素反应，使攻击更加多样化，从而选择您自己的战斗风格！",
